I forget what
it's called.

25:07.667 --> 25:09.333
I think it's called Washington
Crossing The Delaware...

25:09.417 --> 25:11.792
-You didn't forget.
-No.

25:11.875 --> 25:13.625
And do you know why
it's called that?

25:13.709 --> 25:16.166
Because at the moment that
his troops were facing

25:16.250 --> 25:19.125
the sting of battle,
Washington was right there

25:19.208 --> 25:21.375
with them, leaning
into the wind.

25:21.458 --> 25:23.375
Not back at home
jerking off.

25:23.458 --> 25:25.709
I'll admit, Washington Crossing
the Delaware would look pretty

25:25.792 --> 25:27.750
fucking strange without
George Washington.

25:27.834 --> 25:30.709
Then how can you ask me not
to be with my troops right now?

25:30.792 --> 25:34.083
Well, Washington was
allowed to talk to his men.

25:34.166 --> 25:35.250
He was allowed to lead.

25:35.333 --> 25:36.834
When we walk out
of this elevator,

25:36.917 --> 25:40.458
you're gonna see it is
quite a different situation.

25:40.542 --> 25:43.458
But it is what's required
under your deal.

25:49.333 --> 25:51.458
This is Ari Spyros,
Director of Compliance

25:51.542 --> 25:53.792
and Risk Management
for Axe Capital.

25:53.875 --> 25:56.125
It's 12:09 p.m.
I am here with Robert Axelrod

25:56.208 --> 25:58.750
and will stay with him anywhere
he goes inside these walls,

25:58.834 --> 26:02.625
ensuring compliance with his
preclusion from the secur--

26:02.709 --> 26:04.875
I'm looking at small
sugar companies in Asia.

26:04.959 --> 26:07.291
We pick one--invest in it,
grow it, help it.

26:07.375 --> 26:09.834
