Bobby Axelrod doesn't
grow mom-and-pop shops.

26:25.792 --> 26:29.041
He buys 'em out, turns  'em out.

26:29.125 --> 26:32.000
That can't happen
with this one.

26:32.083 --> 26:33.667
Hmm.

26:33.750 --> 26:35.792
Well, then it sounds like your
idea doesn't fucking work.

