coincidences.

27:38.667 --> 27:40.667
If I can
sort you out...

27:40.750 --> 27:42.875
In the last year,
your house was paid off.

27:42.959 --> 27:46.208
Yeah, my wife
came into some money.

27:46.291 --> 27:47.667
Mm.

27:47.750 --> 27:50.417
And your kids, they stopped
taking student loans.

27:50.500 --> 27:52.709
Marcie's dorm room business,
it's really taking off.

27:52.792 --> 27:57.667
I'm sorry, do you...
do you want a towel, or...

27:57.750 --> 28:00.083
-I'm good.
-You're fair.

28:00.166 --> 28:01.750
So, you got sick
from Ice Juice.

28:01.834 --> 28:04.125
The person behind its
poisoning was Bobby Axelrod,

28:04.208 --> 28:07.083
the same man you tried
to cooperate against.

28:07.166 --> 28:09.500
You think he
targeted me deliberately?

28:09.583 --> 28:12.875
Wow, that's a long
road to travel for revenge.

28:12.959 --> 28:15.250
But if he did it,
I hope you nail him.

28:15.333 --> 28:18.250
That juice made me puke
so hard I bust a lung.

28:18.333 --> 28:21.500
Hence the swimming.

