was the only way.

52:34.041 --> 52:36.917
I'm not pulling
the two billion.

52:37.000 --> 52:41.709
It's yours to invest.

52:41.792 --> 52:43.458
I really thought
you didn't trust me.

52:43.542 --> 52:45.000
That's why you
were in the office

52:45.083 --> 52:46.709
looking over
everyone's shoulder.

52:46.792 --> 52:49.250
I was in the office,
because as of now,

52:49.333 --> 52:53.583
I don't know what else
to do with myself.

52:56.166 --> 52:57.250
And...

52:57.333 --> 53:02.000
as much as I can trust anyone
with my name

53:02.083 --> 53:03.709
and my money...

53:03.792 --> 53:06.041
I trust you.

53:06.125 --> 53:07.250
I am irrelevant.

53:07.333 --> 53:10.208
You want the money because you
want the stake, the control.

53:10.291 --> 53:12.959
You need the game
to remember who you are.

53:14.709 --> 53:17.583
I've decided how I'm going
to invest that two billion.

53:17.667 --> 53:21.709
I'm going to diversify,
invest in outside funds.

53:21.792 --> 53:25.125
I'll hear pitches, among them
your hand-picked favorites.

53:25.208 --> 53:26.917
And after I give
them the money,

53:27.000 --> 53:30.250
I'm going to be
a passive investor.

53:30.333 --> 53:32.208
Thank you.

53:39.041 --> 53:41.500
You're not doing this
'cause I need it.

53:41.583 --> 53:43.583
You  need it.

53:44.792 --> 53:49.291
You're giving me a place to play
so I stay off your field.

53:49.375 --> 53:52.417
And you want the benefit
of my moves on our bottom line

53:52.500 --> 53:55.125
in case there's
another disaster.

53:56.834 --> 53:59.959
I'm your hedge.

